column5: Art, Roy, Big Cliff - whatever you did has fixed my problem at least partly.  I can now view and login using my phone. Before, I couldn't even view as a guest. Thank you.  As soon as I get home I'll check to see if I can access the site on my computer.  Thanks again Whiskywizard.
I sent you a e mail please read it for further instructions.   Art
Let us know! We've missed your posts!
